Donate

Rescue is difficult and it never ends. Help us help animals in need through a donation to our PayPal, or donate goods like food or toys by contacting us. We also need your time! Donate volunteer hours and join us on the front lines.

Volunteer

We are always in need of new fosters to #BeTheBridge between the shelter and forever. What you might not know isthat we also need drivers to help us get animals to vet appointments and transport meet-ups, as well as community ambassadors!

Featured Foster

Not all of our animals are adoptable; many are already promised to rescue groups all over the nation. However, we do always have some animals that are available for local adoption. We like to highlight them here so you can fall in love with them as we have!
